OL,3,CJeremy Kyle denies 'belittling' TV
OL,4,Cshow guest at inquest
OL,6,FSteve Dymond, 63, from Portsmouth,
OL,7,FHampshire, is believed to have killed
OL,8,Fhimself seven days after filming for
OL,9,Fthe Jeremy Kyle Show in May 2019.
OL,11,FHe had taken a lie detector test for
OL,12,Fthe programme after being accused of
OL,13,Fcheating on his partner, Jane
OL,14,FCallaghan, from Gosport, Hampshire.
OL,16,FMr Kyle told Winchester Coroner's
OL,17,FCourt that clips from the programme
OL,18,Ffeaturing the case of Mr Dymond and
OL,19,Fhis partner, Jane Callaghan, showed he
OL,20,Fhad "de-escalated... calmed it down".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/19
