OL,6,FHe also denied encouraging the
OL,7,Faudience to take against 63-year-old
OL,8,FMr Dymond, telling the inquest: "Not
OL,9,Fat all - I asked them to give them a
OL,10,Fround of applause."
OL,12,FThe court was shown a number of clips
OL,13,Ffrom the show, including Mr Kyle
OL,14,Ftelling Mr Dymond: "Be a man, grow a
OL,15,Fpair of balls and tell her the goddam
OL,16,Ftruth."
OL,18,FAnother featured the presenter asking
OL,19,F"Has anyone got a shovel?" as Mr
OL,20,FDymond attempted to explain why he had
OL,21,Fbeen messaging another woman.
