OL,6,FJeremy Kyle arrives at Winchester
OL,7,FCoroner's Court on Thursday
OL,9,FRachel Spearing, counsel to the
OL,10,Finquest, asked Mr Kyle on Thursday:
OL,11,F"Do you believe he was humiliated?"
OL,13,FThe broadcaster replied: "I do not,
OL,14,Fand I have read over time apparently I
OL,15,Fcalled him a traitor - I didn't - that
OL,16,Fhe was cowering. I did what I always
OL,17,Fdo and always did, it was what the
OL,18,Fshow... as I understood the show is,
OL,19,Fsad as it might sound, it was a
OL,20,Ftypical part."
