OL,6,FHe added: "It was a show with my name
OL,7,Fon it, with a production team and an
OL,8,Fafter-care team behind it."
OL,10,FDefending his presenting style, Mr
OL,11,FKyle said: "I think that people who
OL,12,Fcame on the show... I think the show
OL,13,Fhad been on air for 15 years, and I
OL,14,Fbelieve the approach for conflict
OL,15,Fresolution was always the same. "Yes,
OL,16,Fit was direct, but it was empathetic,
OL,17,Fit was honest."
