OL,3,CJeremy Kyle denies 'belittling' TV
OL,4,Cshow guest at inquest
OL,6,FHe said: "I want to make a point: I
OL,7,Fhave, in my 14-and-a-half years, not
OL,8,Fbeen involved in the selection of
OL,9,Fguests. I was employed absolutely as
OL,10,Fthe presenter."
OL,12,FHe said he was sent a dossier the
OL,13,Fnight before filming which detailed
OL,14,Fthe approximately 20 guests involved
OL,15,Fin a day's recording.
OL,17,F"I had no involvement in the process
OL,18,Fof selection or anything like that,"
OL,19,Fhe said.
